{"type": "article", "id": 13299, "title": "哪怕身边只有蜡烛和水，也可以给手机充电了", "description": "这主要取决于你对于手机没电的恐惧有多深邃。", "date": "2015-08-11T09:12:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1537, "name": "充电"}, {"id": 817, "name": "众筹"}], "category": 17, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 57, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606003525E90tzskoJ7QFxnij.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span><span>手机没电怎么办？一家名叫 </span><span><span>Flame Stower</span></span><span> 的初创团队认为比这更捉急的是找不到电源为手机充电，为此他们研制出了一款新型充电器，让人们用水和蜡烛为手机充电。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>就像这样。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060035227dDUnyQNv5R38qEz.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56259205\" data-format=\"gif\"><br>\r\n<span></span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>一只 </span><span>Stower</span><span> 蜡烛可以持续燃烧</span><span> 6 </span><span>个小时，足以充满</span><span> 2 </span><span>部 </span><span>iPhone </span><span>手机。其背后的原理是将温度梯度转化为电能。鉴于其 </span><span>2.5w </span><span>的额定功率只有标配充电器的一半，充电速度应该会慢很多了。还有一个小麻烦是，每隔半个小时需要你换一次水。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003523mfYl1UAZvOVQ4qoe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n<span></span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这样一款设计当然不会比充电宝要好用，使用的情景可能会是在万不得已、没有其他办法的情况下，比如：飓风导致的大规模断电——但换句话说，买一台放在家里，这会是你最后的办法。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>除此以外，这款设计同样适用于户外旅行。假设在丛林中，这款充电器应该能派上大用场，设计者还贴心地提醒消费者：用于提供能量的水同时也可以饮用，</span><span>1L </span><span>的水大约煮上</span><span> 1</span><span> 个小时后，就达到饮用的无菌标准了。</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>同样适用于万不得已的时候。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003524148BythGsMTYuAWH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n<span></span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>从官网公布的信息来看，目前有 </span><span>618</span><span> 人对这项设计感兴趣并提供了资助，该项目目前已完成了 </span><span>30,000</span><span> 美金的众筹目标，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/flamestower/candle-charger-emergency-power-generator-for-smart/comments\">本月 </a></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/flamestower/candle-charger-emergency-power-generator-for-smart/comments\"><span>28 </span></a><span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/flamestower/candle-charger-emergency-power-generator-for-smart/comments\">日起接受订购</a>，大概</span><span> 11</span><span> 月可以发货。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}